{"tid":2498832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"現身參拜靖國神社 安倍晉三:為了向為國作戰並犧牲寶貴生命的英靈表達敬意","createTime":"2021-04-21T12:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T12:30:19.000Z","uid":75656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b425b60dc8f8db5f6f36fac979c419e0df7edb8","tid":2498832,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:15:34.000Z","msg":"日本靖國神社今（21日）舉行春季例行大祭，每年靖國神社春祭，日本政府官員是否前往參拜一直是外界關注的焦點，日本首相菅義偉依照去年秋祭方式，僅供奉祭品，不會親自前往神社參拜，不過，前首相安倍晉三則現身神社參拜。<br />\n<br />\n據《共同社》報導，每年4月和10月的春、秋季例大祭，是靖國神社最重要的祭祀活動，由於神社供奉二戰時日本帝國的甲級戰犯，被視為日本昔日軍國主義的象徵，只要日本官員現身都會引發東亞各國極大爭議，今年靖國神社春祭，日本首相菅義偉以「內閣總理大臣 菅義偉」名義供奉了被稱為「真榊」的供品。<br />\n<br />\n除菅義偉外，厚生勞動大臣田村憲久、萬博大臣井上信治這次也有供奉「真榊」。<br />\n<br />\n而日本前首相安倍晉三則現身靖國神社參拜，他在參拜後向媒體表示：「為了向為國作戰並犧牲寶貴生命的英靈表達敬意進行了參拜。」安倍從2012年12月再度執政以來，每年的春、秋季例大祭都會供奉祭品，其任職首相期間，只在2013年12月參拜過一次靖國神社。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3506419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3506419&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=50f350d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3506419&h=1be10aeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3506419</a>"},{"pid":"76e187819cfcc60adf7a719b4e71e6c469de0121","tid":2498832,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"Respect 🙏🏻"},{"pid":"4600c747a4662a734d0133acb6ed4ecaa8484cca","tid":2498832,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"獻上心臟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668466d56583f91b47ada34447c8cf024d291390","tid":2498832,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"日本義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e65eeab1d42310fff384e6749701b8d49becc7","tid":2498832,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"靖國神社唔只得二戰班戰犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caea97d90c1427738dc89b98c99cace7d710be4","tid":2498832,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"如果日本當年統治到支那就唔會有今日咁嘅局面"},{"pid":"ca4387d253743578ba45b9add75aba40ef25bc43","tid":2498832,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3e65eeab1d42310fff384e6749701b8d49becc7","tid":2498832,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"靖國神社唔只得二戰班戰犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"係 好多人唔知道呢點<br />\n<br />\n甚至裡面有好多外國人 例如 台灣人就有3萬在裡面供奉"}]}